				<p class="font-light mt-3 transition-colors hover:text-blue-700">Paga tus compras de forma rápida y segura.</p>
				<p class="bg-blue-200 transition-colors hover:bg-blue-300 mt-6 text-xs font-semibold text-blue-700 mr-5 ml-5 h-6 rounded-md flex items-center justify-center">Conocer medios de pago</p>
			</div>
			<div class="bg-white rounded w-72 h-72 hover:cursor-pointer shadow-md">
				<p class="mt-3">Menos de $40.000</p>
				<img class="h-28 mt-3 mx-auto" src="https://http2.mlstatic.com/frontend-assets/homes-palpatine/dynamic-access-desktop/low-price-product.svg">
				<p class="font-light mt-3 transition-colors hover:text-blue-700">Descubre productos de precios bajos.</p>
				<p class="bg-blue-200 transition-colors hover:bg-blue-300 mt-6 text-xs font-semibold text-blue-700 mr-5 ml-5 h-6 rounded-md flex items-center justify-center">Mostrar productos</p>
			</div>
			<div class="bg-white rounded w-72 h-72  hover:cursor-pointer shadow-md">
				<p class="mt-3">Compra protegida</p>
				<img class="h-28 mt-3 mx-auto" src="https://http2.mlstatic.com/frontend-assets/homes-palpatine/dynamic-access-desktop/buy-protected.svg">
				<p class="font-light mt-3 transition-colors hover:text-blue-700">Puedes devolver tu compra gratis.</p>
				<p class="bg-blue-200 transition-colors hover:bg-blue-300 mt-6 text-xs font-semibold text-blue-700 mr-5 ml-5 h-6 rounded-md flex items-center justify-center">Como funciona</p>	
